ZH: 我们必须按时纳税。
EN: We must pay taxes on time.

ZH: 政府要求每个公民纳税。
EN: The government requires every citizen to pay taxes.

ZH: 纳税是每个公民的责任。
EN: Paying taxes is the responsibility of every citizen.

ZH: 我们需要合理地纳税。
EN: We need to pay taxes reasonably.

ZH: 他们拒绝纳税并面临法律后果。
EN: They refused to pay taxes and faced legal consequences.

ZH: 这家公司逃税数百万元。
EN: This company has evaded millions of yuan in taxes.

ZH: 居民需要纳税来支持公共服务。
EN: Residents need to pay taxes to support public services.

ZH: 每年都有新税法要求纳税人遵守。
EN: Every year, new tax laws require taxpayers to comply.

ZH: 纳税是国家财政的重要来源。
EN: Paying taxes is an important source of national finance.

ZH: 我们应该诚实地纳税避免罚款。
EN: We should pay taxes honestly to avoid fines.

ZH: 他们愿意纳税来保证社会稳定。
EN: They are willing to pay taxes to ensure social stability.

ZH: 纳税人有义务提供准确的纳税资料。
EN: Taxpayers are obligated to provide accurate tax information.

ZH: 如果你不纳税，你将被起诉。
EN: If you don't pay taxes, you will be prosecuted.

ZH: 希望政府能够透明地使用纳税人的金钱。
EN: Hope the government can transparently use taxpayers' money.

ZH: 我们需尊重纳税人的努力和贡献。
EN: We need to respect the efforts and contributions of taxpayers.

ZH: 纳税是我们对社会的回馈。
EN: Paying taxes is our way of giving back to society.

ZH: 民众应该知道纳税的重要性。
EN: The public should know the importance of paying taxes.

ZH: 纳税是作为一个公民的义务。
EN: Paying taxes is a duty as a citizen.

ZH: 老师们在教育学生纳税的重要性。
EN: Teachers are educating students on the importance of paying taxes.
